{"tid":556990,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有個巴打開左汽車美容，今日親自去試下live","createTime":"2018-02-11T03:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T23:30:00.000Z","uid":10840,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4071132f52c05a890d3bbac63f56e3d4592ff509","tid":556990,"uid":10840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:04:17.000Z","msg":"半年之前新車落地，即刻搵左間美容公司幫部車鍍膜，結果頭一星期效果係幾好，但一個月唔夠，就充滿淚痕，沖水都沖唔走(鍍膜正常會沖水就得)。<br />\n<br />\n之後成部車重無啦啦有好多黑色膠痕岀現，用指甲整得甩，但太多，所以拖到見到巴打開po，膽粗粗試下佢打蠟既手勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/110336_c981a90038dc11c134825e35defa0d7f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F110336_c981a90038dc11c134825e35defa0d7f.jpeg&h=114d3c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭尾都充滿膠痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e94c265db223db4e05867b0cd7ff175e651a96","tid":556990,"uid":134806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T23:30:00.000Z","msg":"Live？"}]}